US rapper, Earl Simmons, popularly known as DMX is dead. The iconic rapper’s death was announced on Friday. He died at the age of 50 after suffering a heart attack. According to the hospital in White Plains, New York, where he got admitted after he had suffered a drug overdose and heart attack, DMX died from “catastrophic cardiac arrests For the past week, DMX had been on life support with fans, families praying and showing support at the hospital. Earlier, reports of his death were refuted by his management. DAILY POST had earlier reported that the 50-year-old rapper was rushed to a hospital in White Plains, New York, on Friday night after experiencing a heart attack triggered by a drug overdose. 